<L>__{interior museum new painting night}
<A>__{it's a beautiful painting in the high renaissance style depicting four archangels hovering protectively over a cherubic baby. one holds a harp, one, an olive branch, the third, a book, and the last, a sword. most remarkably, their faces bear an uncanny resemblance to venkman, stantz, spengler and winston.}
